{
  "texts": [
    "Future ResearchWhile this study focuses on a specific design case in AAC, it opens the door to a variety of promising research avenues in materials science and the application of LLMs.",
    "The concept of inverse design, combining initial suggestions with systematic iterative improvements, stands out as a key area for evaluating the capabilities of LLMs.",
    "The challenge here is to achieve both, a robust initial performance and continuous improvement of subsequent proposals.",
    "A critical takeaway from our research is the significant potential for enhancing the domain-specific capabilities of LLMs in materials science through relatively generic post-training measures.",
    "This enhancement involves refining the context quality and extending TT in conjunction with a VM."
  ]
}